  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> and <strong>1 SP</strong> to perform a debilitating strike on a creature using a Light Weapon.</p>\n<p>Make an <strong>Attack Check </strong>against the target, and it makes a <strong>Physical Save </strong>against your Save DC.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Attack Hit: </strong>It takes your Weapon damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Save&nbsp;Failure: </strong>Until the end of your next turn, it suffers 1 effect of your choice:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Exposed </strong>(Attack Checks against it have ADV)</li>\n<li><strong>Deafened </strong>(it cannot hear)</li>\n<li><strong>Hindered </strong>(it has DisADV on Attack Checks)</li>\n<li><strong>Slowed 1</strong> (every 1 Space it moves costs an extra 1 Space of movement)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip:&nbsp;</strong>You can add Weapon to use together with that Feature. Select it on&nbsp;<strong>Details&nbsp;</strong>Tab of that&nbsp;<strong>Feature</strong>.</em></p>",
